<view class="page"><view class="header"><text class="title">车辆信息</text></view><view class="map-container"><map class="map" latitude="{{a}}" longitude="{{b}}" scale="{{c}}" markers="{{d}}" polygons="{{e}}" show-location="{{true}}" bindmarkertap="{{f}}"></map></view><view class="info-card"><view class="info-row"><text class="info-label">车辆编号</text><text class="info-value">{{g}}</text></view><view class="info-row"><text class="info-label">车辆状态</text><text class="info-value">{{h}}</text></view><view class="info-row"><text class="info-label">故障状态</text><text class="info-value">{{i}}</text></view><view class="info-row"><text class="info-label">剩余电量</text><text class="info-value">{{j}}</text></view></view><view class="tip-card"><text class="tip-text">扫码解锁成功后，可直接停放当前车辆，或继续扫码解锁下一辆。</text></view><view class="action-section"><view class="action-row"><button class="action-btn secondary-btn" hover-class="button-hover" hover-start-time="0" hover-stay-time="90" disabled="{{l}}" bindtap="{{m}}">{{k}}</button><button class="action-btn primary-btn" hover-class="button-hover" hover-start-time="0" hover-stay-time="90" disabled="{{o}}" bindtap="{{p}}">{{n}}</button></view><button class="manual-btn" hover-class="button-hover" hover-start-time="0" hover-stay-time="90" bindtap="{{q}}"> 编号开锁 </button></view></view>